20 10 translate

72 dup scale
0.01 setlinewidth

/P[
 [0 0] 
 [0.5 1.6] 
 [1 1.4]
 [1.5 0] 
 [0.5 0.9] 
 [0.9 0.6] 
 [0.8 0.2] 
] def

newpath
P 3 get aload pop moveto
P 0 get aload pop lineto
P 1 get aload pop lineto
P 2 get aload pop lineto
closepath
gsave
0.8 setgray
% fill
grestore
% stroke

0 1 P length 1 sub {
/i exch def
newpath
P i get aload pop 0.032 0 360 arc
fill
} for



